author: Ken Dilanian and Courtney Kube
title: US intel community examining whether coronavirus emerged accidentally from a Chinese lab
description: One expert said the theory the virus came from a Wuhan animal market has lost favor in some quarters, in part because an early patient had no market link.
content:
The U.S. intelligence community is examining whether the virus that caused a global pandemic emerged accidentally from a Chinese research lab studying diseases in bats, current and former U.S. intelligence officials tell NBC News.
